{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/berani-bermimpi-yuk-bantu-wujudkan-mimpi-adik-adik-kita/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Berani Bermimpi: Yuk Bantu Wujudkan Mimpi Adik-adik Kita!","content":"\n<p>Sebelumnya, CIAYO Comics bersama Gerakkan Indonesia berpartisipasi dalam acara <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ciayo-comics-berbagi-di-ramadan-berani/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Kakak Adik berbagi 2019 (opens in a new tab)\">Kakak Adik berbagi 2019</a>. Di acara ini, adik-adik dari berbagai yayasan yatim-piatu se-Jabodetabek berkumpul untuk bermain dan berbagi mimpi. Kisah mereka yang penuh mimpi dan harapan menjadi inspirasi bagi CIAYO Comics dan para author komik untuk menciptakan Berani Bermimpi, sebuah antologi komik pendek.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53901\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/berani-bermimpi-yuk-bantu-wujudkan-mimpi-adik-adik-kita/attachment/02-berani-bermimpi/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-berani-bermimpi.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-berani-bermimpi\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-berani-bermimpi-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-berani-bermimpi.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-berani-bermimpi.jpg\" alt=\"Cerita mereka akan tampil dalam antologi komik Berani Bermimpi. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures\" class=\"wp-image-53901\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-berani-bermimpi.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-berani-bermimpi-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Cerita mereka akan tampil dalam antologi komik Berani Bermimpi. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Di dalam antologi Berani Bermimpi, ada 14 komik yang terinspirasi dari kisah dan mimpi adik-adik di acara Kakak Adik berbagi 2019. Misalnya ada Caroline yang ingin jadi Polwan, Anna Maria yang ingin jadi tentara, hingga Defa yang ingin jadi insinyur. Mimpi adik-adik kita kemudian diwujudkan ke dalam bentuk komik yang tidak hanya menghibur, namun juga menginspirasi dan memberi semangat! </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Baca juga: </strong><a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ciayo-comics-berbagi-di-ramadan-berani/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"CIAYO Comics x Gerakan Indonesia, Wujudkan Mimpi dalam #RamadanBeran (opens in a new tab)\">CIAYO Comics x Gerakan Indonesia, Wujudkan Mimpi dalam #RamadanBeran</a>i</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53902\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/berani-bermimpi-yuk-bantu-wujudkan-mimpi-adik-adik-kita/attachment/03-berani-bermimpi/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/03-berani-bermimpi.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-berani-bermimpi\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/03-berani-bermimpi-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/03-berani-bermimpi.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/03-berani-bermimpi.jpg\" alt=\"Dafa ingin jadi insinyur... bisa nggak ya? Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-53902\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/03-berani-bermimpi.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/03-berani-bermimpi-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Dafa ingin jadi insinyur&#8230; bisa nggak ya? Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Seperti apa kisah-kisahnya? Yuk kita lihat satu-satu! Pertama ada kisahnya Defa dalam komik Engine Knight’s Partner karya Ai Shuma (<a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/bhurloka\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Bhurloka (opens in a new tab)\">Bhurloka</a>). Dalam komik ini, Defa bingung ingin menulis cita-cita apa untuk tugas sekolahnya. Ia ingin jadi insinyur seperti Engine Knight, superhero favoritnya. Tapi ia tidak yakin bisa mewujudkannya. </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53903\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/berani-bermimpi-yuk-bantu-wujudkan-mimpi-adik-adik-kita/attachment/04-berani-bermimpi/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/04-berani-bermimpi.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-berani-bermimpi\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/04-berani-bermimpi-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/04-berani-bermimpi.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/04-berani-bermimpi.jpg\" alt=\"Engine Knight menolong Dafa! Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-53903\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/04-berani-bermimpi.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/04-berani-bermimpi-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Engine Knight menolong Dafa! Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Tak disangka-sangka, ia melihat langsung pertarungan Engine\nKnight! Engine Knight kewalahan melawan Dr. Pralaya yang terlalu kuat dan\nhampir saja kalah. Pertemuan Defa dengan Engine Knight ternyata memberikan\ninspirasi dan secara tidak langsung menolong Engine Knight dalam\npertempurannya!</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53904\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/berani-bermimpi-yuk-bantu-wujudkan-mimpi-adik-adik-kita/attachment/05-berani-bermimpi/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/05-berani-bermimpi.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-berani-bermimpi\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/05-berani-bermimpi-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/05-berani-bermimpi.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/05-berani-bermimpi.jpg\" alt=\"Anna takut ditembak. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-53904\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/05-berani-bermimpi.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/05-berani-bermimpi-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Anna takut ditembak. Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Komik kedua dari Anna Maria digambar oleh Kathrinna Rakhmavika (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Gastronomale (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/gastronomale\" target=\"_blank\">Gastronomale</a>). Dalam komik ini Anna yang ingin jadi tentara “ditakut-takuti” temannya. Menjadi bimbang dan kurang percaya diri, Anna bermimpi bertemu dengan tentara perempuan saat tidur. Sang tentara perempuan meyakinkan Anna jika ia bisa menjadi seorang tentara perempuan.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53905\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/berani-bermimpi-yuk-bantu-wujudkan-mimpi-adik-adik-kita/attachment/06-berani-bermimpi/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/06-berani-bermimpi.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-berani-bermimpi\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/06-berani-bermimpi-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/06-berani-bermimpi.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/06-berani-bermimpi.jpg\" alt=\"Kakak tentara perempuan itu, siapa dia ya? Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-53905\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/06-berani-bermimpi.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/06-berani-bermimpi-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Kakak tentara perempuan itu, siapa dia ya? Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Selain dua komik di atas, masih ada lagi komik-komik lainnya yang terinspirasi dari kisah adik-adik kita. Seperti apa kisahnya? Nantikan kemunculannya hanya di <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/berani-bermimpi\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"CIAYO Comics (opens in a new tab)\">CIAYO Comics</a>! Jangan lupa untuk di-<em>subscribe</em>, ya.</p>\n\n\n\n<iframe src=\"https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fblog.ciayo%2Fvideos%2F372808573577505%2F&#038;show_text=0&#038;width=560\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden\" scrolling=\"no\" frameborder=\"0\" allowTransparency=\"true\" allowFullScreen=\"true\"></iframe>\n\n\n\n<p>Eits, nggak cuma itu saja loh! <strong>Setiap komik yang kamu <em>likes</em> akan diubah menjadi sesuatu yang bermanfaat bagi adik-adik kita dalam mewujudkan mimpinya.</strong> Keren, kan? Mumpung sekarang bulan Ramadhan, mari berlomba-lomba membantu adik-adik kita yang membutuhkan! Buktikan kalau kamu #BeraniBermimpi!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"b1f3a2fd-b358-5ed1-8d32-18a7343f595a"}}}